vulnerability.description: App cs4295.memecreator puts data (retrieved from an Explicit Intent (Component = ReceiveIntentActivity)) on an unsafe sink (LOG) in one of its components (cs4295.memecreator.ReceiveIntentActivity). A malicious app can send a sensitive data from this channel.

App csd.qtproject.minesweeper puts data (retrieved from an Explicit Intent (Component = QtActivity)) on an unsafe sink (LOG) in one of its components (org.qtproject.qt5.android.bindings.QtActivity). A malicious app can send a sensitive data from this channel.

App net.justdave.nwsweatheralertswidget puts data (retrieved from an Explicit Intent (Component = NWSWidgetProvider)) on an unsafe sink (LOG) in one of its components (net.justdave.nwsweatheralertswidget.NWSWidgetProvider). A malicious app can send a sensitive data from this channel.

App net.justdave.nwsweatheralertswidget puts data (retrieved from an Explicit Intent (Component = DebugActivity)) on an unsafe sink (LOG) in one of its components (net.justdave.nwsweatheralertswidget.DebugActivity). A malicious app can send a sensitive data from this channel.

App net.justdave.nwsweatheralertswidget puts data (retrieved from an Explicit Intent (Component = MainActivity)) on an unsafe sink (LOG) in one of its components (net.justdave.nwsweatheralertswidget.MainActivity). A malicious app can send a sensitive data from this channel.
